{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act26side_level_act26side_st02","storyGroup":"act26side","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"act26side_level_act26side_06_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HE-ST-2","storyName":"在花园里","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"沉默的圣徒拾起那枝花茎断折，花瓣焚毁的花。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act26side/level_act26side_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act26side_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["爱琳","杰拉尔德","克莱芒","费德里科","艾伦戴尔","艾丝塔拉"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_bg_39_g2_abandonsancturay.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":5},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.8","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"快来看这个，霍斯特！这边，你看！","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"居然真在圣像前种上花了，而且总觉得这里的花开得比其他地方更漂亮哦？克莱芒那家伙脾气虽然软了点，但还是有点本领的嘛！","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"真亏斯特凡诺能同意，又是挖圣堂地板，又是到处找土什么的......连用什么土都这么讲究。","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"慢点跑，别忘记你身上还有伤。","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"这点小伤算什么？","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"小伤也有恶化的风险。","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"还有，现在别再叫那个名字了，叫我杰拉尔德。","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"好了好了，知道了！你怎么也开始管东管西了......可别和斯特凡诺学这个啊！","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"斯特凡诺那老头子就是管得太多，所以才长那么多皱纹。","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"老人家就得放宽心，少操心少管事，这样才能长寿！","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"爱琳！说得太过了，斯特凡诺只是一心为修道院的将来打算。","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我们能像现在这样住下，也多亏了他。","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"我知道！我只是说他打算得太多了，我看了都替他觉得累得慌！","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"就怕他哪天扛不住了，受不了了，那是要吃大苦头的......！","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"斯特凡诺不会听劝，他在萨科塔里应该也是特别固执的那一类，只要是他认准了的道理，就一定会坚持到底。","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"不过，我们能在这里定居下来，也多亏了他的这一点。","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"他说我们萨卡兹和其他人没什么不同......","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"老头子这话说得没错啊。","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"算了，要是真有他扛不住了的那天，大不了你我帮忙搭把手，替他撑着......也算是报恩了。","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"你也别再想之前的事了。我们那时离开卡兹戴尔，已经背弃了特蕾西娅殿下......杰拉尔德，我们回不了头了。","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"你我都是。","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......我知道。","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"不用这样提醒我，爱琳。","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我曾追随殿下，但不知道什么时候起，我不再能看见殿下描绘的图景......在卡兹戴尔的两位殿下身上，我找不到我们萨卡兹的未来。","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"别难过。","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我没事。至少现在，我们已经有了新的生活。","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我把愿意离开的人带出卡兹戴尔，就会对他们负起责任。","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"现在这日子......比从前好多了。","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"别大意，我们现在和从前不同，没有物资支持，那些强盗里偶尔也有不好对付的。","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"你是不是也太小心了一点？","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"搞不好几年、十几年之后，凶名赫赫的雇佣兵都要变成乡下猎户咯。哈哈哈哈！","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"哈哈哈哈......","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"......那个，我说，杰拉尔德啊。","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"嗯？","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"你想过你真的放下武器，变成乡下猎户会是什么样吗？","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱琳","text":"到时候我又会变成什么样？","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"没有。我没想过。","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"那时候的我会变成什么样......","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"爱琳，如果你愿意，你可以亲自确认。","id":48},{"type":"dialog","id":49},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"charslot","id":52},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":54},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":55},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":56},{"type":"text","text":"很久以前，在与人拼杀后的深夜，杰拉尔德总会在想要喘口气时放任自己抬头看天。","id":57},{"type":"text","text":"天空是压抑的黑色，篝火渐熄，火焰逐渐冷却。","id":58},{"type":"text","text":"战场上浑身染血的雇佣兵擦掉身上脸上的脏污，注视着同样伤痕累累的同伴，短暂地思考过某些对于他们来说有些奢侈的问题。","id":59},{"type":"text","text":"他们这样的萨卡兹，是否真的能够拥有所谓幸福的一生？","id":60},{"type":"text","text":"他曾坚信萨卡兹重新拥有家的那天一定会来，只是他感到越来越无力，越来越力不从心。","id":61},{"type":"text","text":"他们流了太多血。在实现那位殿下的美好愿景前，他们的血就快要流尽了。","id":62},{"type":"text","text":"杰拉尔德终于决定放下卡兹戴尔的一切，他带上那些快要活不下去的人，逃一样地离开了曾经为之拼命的土地。","id":63},{"type":"text","text":"他们隐姓埋名，终于找到一处能容他们萨卡兹安身的场所，他们只期盼在这里过上平静的、与常人无异的生活。","id":64},{"type":"text","text":"这个愿望一度得以实现。","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"但是到底是从什么时候开始，生活开始变得苦涩，开始无法呼吸？","id":66},{"type":"text","text":"就好像是放在台子上无人品尝的佳肴。","id":67},{"type":"text","text":"明明努力维持，没人破坏，却还是变了质。","id":68},{"type":"text","text":"如果只有鲜血能让这一切结束......","id":69},{"type":"text","text":"那么我所能做的事，就只剩下这么一件。","id":70},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"charslot","id":74},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","id":76},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":79},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"克莱芒，你不必再劝我。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我不能走，也走不了。","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我从没告诉过你我之前的名字，那不是什么值得回味的过去，不过是个丧家之犬，一个臭名昭著的逃兵。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"有我在，他们就有理由对其他人动手。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"别这副表情，我只是先一步去见爱琳，这没什么，死亡对我这样曾经刀口舔血的人来说并不算太陌生。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"如果用我的脑袋就能交换其他人的生路，也算是值得。","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我走之后，你不用担心这里剩下的人，他们会听我的话。","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"莱蒙德还年轻，恐怕他会有点冲动。到时候......就拜托你多劝劝。","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fd/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"最后......","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"帮我转告斯特凡诺，或许最开始我们在荒野上流浪那会，就不该贸然停下，不该尝试留下来。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"只是对我，对我们萨卡兹来说，这里实在太好了......","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"能一起生活这么多年，一切真像是一场梦，但我清楚我们终究要面对现实。","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"替我向斯特凡诺说一句——谢谢，我很抱歉。","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"接下来就拜托你了，克莱芒。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":100},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_926_1#4$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":101},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"到了最后，还是以这个身份......","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我究竟是个猎户，还是......依然是那个雇佣兵？","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"抱歉，爱琳，我现在的样子，恐怕你看了也不会感到满意吧。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_926_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":109},{"type":"charslot","id":110},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_bg_39_g3_abandonsancturay_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":114},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":115,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"......天亮了。","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"从昨天到今天，好像发生了很多事。但又好像只是一眨眼，一切就都结束了。","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"不管怎么说......这个夜晚确实漫长，不是吗？","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":122},{"type":"charslot","id":123},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":124},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":126},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你在做什么？","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"不是什么值得您过问的事，费德里科先生。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我只是想找一朵花，杰拉尔德总不能空着手去见爱琳，这不太好。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"不过，我好像......昨晚的那场大火把东西都烧没了，什么都没剩下。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"如果你只是想要鲜花，不必特地来这里。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"您不清楚，费德里科先生，那不一样。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"这里的花是特别的。它们是这座修道院培育出来的特殊品种......","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"象征友谊与希望。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"是的，友谊与希望。主教阁下曾告诉我，这是拉特兰与伊比利亚携手合作的象征，是修道院最重要的东西之一......","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"多好啊......当时的我，立刻就被它们迷住了。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"那个时候修道院里还到处都是成片种植的花卉，每到花期，从钟塔那样的高处往下看，整座修道院就像是被花填满。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"爱琳特别喜欢那种风景，杰拉尔德也喜欢......","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"有很多人原本很怕萨卡兹，不敢和他们说话，但在经过一次花期后，彼此之间的关系就变好了很多。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"大家发现，原来就算是传闻中冷酷好斗的萨卡兹，也会在路过花圃时，停下步子看一小会，也会尝试摘一两朵，装饰在家中。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"他们看起来一点也不像是什么凶恶的亡命之徒，他们和我们没什么不同......","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这里还有一朵。","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"嗯？啊......您说的是圣像下面的这一朵吗？","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我看到它了，它很幸运，应该是正好被倒下的圣像压住，才能像这样保存下来......","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"但是很可惜，它不是我想要的那一朵。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"理由？","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"您看这朵花......看看它，难道您还不明白吗？","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"就算躲藏在圣像之下得以幸存，它的花茎却早已折断，花瓣也被火焰燎烤，它已经伤痕累累了。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"但它还在。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"是吗，它真的还在吗？","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我之前也相信，有些东西可以扛过风吹日晒，不怕刀山火海。请不要笑话我......我曾经真心相信过。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"那个时候，尽管生活依然不算轻松，但一切好像都还很好。","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"只要有一点余裕，妮娜大婶就会给孩子们做些小点心。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"您听过青草格子饼吗？","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"妮娜大婶和赫曼一起，用从拉特兰带来的配方，加上萨卡兹栽培的香草，做出了大家都喜欢的、独属于修道院的甜点。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"妮娜大婶总是说，我们大人苦一点没什么，可是我们的孩子们，他们不能只知道“苦”的滋味。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"孩子们需要知道什么是“甜”......","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......我会记住这种甜点。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"哈哈，不重要了，我们已经忘记甜味太久......","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"事到如今，恐怕已经没有人会特地再去做一份格子饼了。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"费德里科先生，有的时候我会感到好奇。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"如果萨科塔没有那么特殊，如果拉特兰都是如我一样，最平凡、最普通、最不值一提的人......","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"那座圣城，还会是如今这般模样吗？","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"拉特兰，还会是拉特兰吗？","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......我不知道。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"真遗憾。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"克莱芒，你......","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你已经不再相信——你已经改变想法了吗？","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我只是不得不看到现实。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"许多东西并没有人们想的那样牢不可破，考验只会让它受伤。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"而只要有了一点瑕疵，混入了一丁点异物，哪怕只是有一点不起眼的伤痕，都再也没法修复，没法挽回......","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"就像您发现的那朵花，费德里科先生。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"这里已经没有我想要的花了。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"快要到晨会的时间了，我也该走了。","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"再见，费德里科先生。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":203},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":204},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":205},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":206},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":207},{"type":"dialog","id":208},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":209},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":210},{"type":"charslot","id":211},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":213},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":217},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":220},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"100","yFrom":"50","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":221},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":222},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_monastery_nomal.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":223,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":224},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":225},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科·吉亚洛独自留在这个清晨的圣堂。","id":226},{"type":"text","text":"火灾留下的痕迹已经过简单处理，失去了原有摆设的圣堂内越发空旷，只有脚步声独自回荡。","id":227},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科是一位优秀的公证所执行者，这是他成为执行者的第六年，工作早已得心应手。","id":228},{"type":"text","text":"同时，这也是他被加上圣徒名号的第一个年头，没有人能给他启发或指点。","id":229},{"type":"text","text":"沉默的圣徒拾起那枝花茎断折，花瓣焚毁的花。","id":230},{"type":"text","text":"圣像给予其庇护，让其免于被火焰吞噬，在那样的大火中，它的幸存是某种奇迹。","id":231},{"type":"text","text":"可在另一个人眼中，这份奇迹一文不值。","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"花还在。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"却不是想要的那一朵？","id":236,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不可修复的伤痕......","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"无法理解。","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"拉特兰是否还会是拉特兰......？","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"............","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"可参考的数据不足，无法得出答案。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":244},{"type":"text","text":"执行者费德里科在这时忽然意识到——","id":245},{"type":"text","text":"克莱芒的神色实在是太过平静了。","id":246},{"type":"text","text":"他既没有提起杰拉尔德的死，也没有提起其他萨卡兹的安排。","id":247},{"type":"text","text":"而自己呢？","id":248},{"type":"text","text":"不伴随行动的言语毫无力量，所以他不会说一定会找出真相。","id":249},{"type":"text","text":"也不会说，自己一定会完成杰拉尔德最后的请求。","id":250},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科注视着眼前残破的花。","id":251},{"type":"text","text":"他有所预感——","id":252},{"type":"text","text":"总有一天，自己所怀有的疑问，能够在这朵花上得到解答。","id":253},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":256},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":257},{"type":"charslot","id":258},{"type":"image","id":259},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":260},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":261},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_normal_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":262,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"嗯——哈噢唔——","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"早上啦......萨拉，该起床啦......","id":266,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"唔，唔呣唔呣，呼......","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_929_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"艾伦，艾伦！醒一醒，艾伦——","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6e/Avg_avg_npc_929_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"别睡啦，妈妈，妈妈昨天回来啦！","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6e/Avg_avg_npc_929_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_929_1#8$1","focus":"all","id":273},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":274},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovementsp","volume":"0.8","id":275},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_928_1#4$1","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.8","isblock":"false","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":277},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_928_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"欸？！","id":279,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"妈妈回来了吗？在哪里在哪里？","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_929_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"嗯！一定是妈妈，你看——","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6e/Avg_avg_npc_929_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.7","id":284},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":285},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_928_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"哇！这是妈妈给我们的新毯子吗？但是破破的......","id":287,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_928_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"不过上面还有圈圈的图案呢！还有长翅膀的小人......嗯，没错，这是妈妈之前说会给我们带的！","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/64/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_929_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"破一点也没关系呀，我们是好孩子，要体谅妈妈啦，妈妈自己的衣服都破破的......","id":291,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3d/Avg_avg_npc_929_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_928_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"好啦，我当然知道嘛。","id":293,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"走吧，我们去找费德里科哥哥！","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_929_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"今天也能和费德里科哥哥一起玩吗......？","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6e/Avg_avg_npc_929_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_928_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"笨笨，我们是要去告诉费德里科哥哥，妈妈晚上有回来看我们，让费德里科哥哥不要担心啦~","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_928_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":299},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":301},{"type":"charslot","id":302},{"type":"image","id":303}],"characters":["爱琳","杰拉尔德","克莱芒","费德里科","艾伦戴尔","艾丝塔拉"]}